### API Testing Requests
### Save as requests.rest and use with REST Client extension

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@studentBatch = AA22-105
@studentNic = 200012345678
@staffEmail = finance@example.com
@staffPassword = password123

### Student Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/student/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchNumber": "{{studentBatch}}",
  "nic": "{{studentNic}}"
}

### Staff Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/staff/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{staffEmail}}",
  "password": "{{staffPassword}}"
}

### Get Profile (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}
